          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is a short manual outlining ceremonies for digging ground for a new house, prescribing the setting up and worship of various images of gods, and especially for appeasing (śanti) evils and calamities that might befall the occupants of the house. Manuscript lacks beginning.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
